--installing ruby on rvm
http://tecadmin.net/install-ruby-on-rails-on-ubuntu/

--creating gemset
rvm gemset create rails4.2 (name of the gem)
rvm use ruby-2.2.4@rails4.2

--making ruby default
rvm use ruby 2.2.4 --default


-- installing spreadsheet
sudo gem install spreadsheet








